These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: hamster, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Pet   | hamster  | cat |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, dancer
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Job   | security-guard | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Pet   | lizard | rabbit   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, indonesian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, march
1. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | french  | indonesian |
| Birthday         | june | march    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, march
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Birthday      | november | march |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | crime  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
