.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-9::.
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, swisher
1. the brazilian is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Nationality   | colombian | brazilian |
| Cigar           | bongani    | swisher     |

